'''Elmo Clifford Gideon''' (January 11, 1924 – December 21, 2010) was an American painter and sculptor of the 20th and 21st centuries.

Thursday, April 12, 2001 was declared “Gideon Day” with an official Proclamation by the [[Miami-Dade County]] Office of the Mayor and Board of County Commissioners.<ref>[http://www.miamidade.gov/govaction/matter.asp?matter=010823&file=false&yearFolder=Y2001 "Gideon Day." Miami-Dade County Proclamation. Online. 2001]</ref>

